quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  27,14,Mitima yawo idadziwa kuti zizindikiro zidali zoona koma adazikana izo chifukwa chakulakwa ndiponso kunyada kwawo. Taona zimene zidawaonekera anthu olakwa
  27,15,"Ndithudi Ife tidapereka nzeru kwa Davide ndi Solomoni. Iwo adati, “Kuyamikidwa ndi kwa Iye amene watikweza ife kukhala pamwamba pa akapolo ake ambiri okhulupirira.”"
  27,16,"Solomoniadalowam’malomwaDavide.Iye adati, “Oh inu anthu anga! Ife taphunzitsidwa chiyankhulo cha mbalame ndipo tapatsidwa zinthu zabwino zambiri. Ndithudi ichi ndi chifundo choonekeratu.”"
  27,17,"Asirikali a nkhondo a mtundu wa majini, anthu ena ndi mbalame anasonkhanitsidwa pamaso pa Solomoni ndipo adaimitsidwa pa mizere m’magulu osiyanasiyana mogwirizana ndi maudindo"
  27,18,"Mpaka pamene iwo anafika pa chigwa cha nyerere, nyerere ina idati, “Oh inu nyerere! Lowani ku maenje anu chifukwa mwina Solomoni pamodzi ndi Asirikali ake, akhoza kukuonongani mosadziwa.”"
  27,19,"Solomoni adamwetulira posangalatsidwa ndi mawu ake ndipo iye adati, “Ndilangizeni Ambuye kuti ndizikuthokozani pa zabwino zonse zimene mwandipatsa ine ndi makolo anga ndiponso kuti ndizichita ntchito zabwino zimene zimakukondweretsani inu. Ndilowetseni ine ku Paradiso kudzera m’chisomo chanu, kuti ndikhale pakati pa akapolo anu angwiro.”"
  27,20,"Iye adayendera mbalame nati, “Kodi mbalame yotchedwa mnthengu ili kuti? Kodi kapena iyo ili pamodzi ndi amene sadabwere?”"
  27,21,“Ndithudi ndidzailanga iyo ndi chilango chowawa kapena ndidzaipha kupatula ngati ibweretsa kwa ine chifukwa chomveka.”
  27,22,"Ndipo mbalame ya mnthengu siidachedwe ndipo idati, “Ndadziwa zimene iwe siudziwa ndipo ndikubweretsera nkhani yoona kuchokera ku Saba.”"